Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:49.89,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}今夜星空 又添幾顆傷心淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:52.84,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}靜靜守望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.82,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}次時代的寵兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:59.42,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}擁抱天宇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.42,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}無盡的痛苦深處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:11.90,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}飄渺的希望初生始動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:19.82,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}預示指引漫漫前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:23.54,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}你心目中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:27.44,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}喚醒未來的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.55,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}破壞 再生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:34.45,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}誕生 衰亡 進化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:38.24,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}週而復始 無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:39.92,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:42.82,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}即便光明失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:48.06,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}寄托思念的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:53.93,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,600)}永不改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有人認為這太魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否同去 希望你們自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也願意去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部門全員一致想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛逃者 古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即給我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓UE為所欲為下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營救叛逃者的你們也是叛逃者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊的準備完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙裏照樣可以抓他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:01:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出航準備進行得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 即將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦10分鐘後 從衛星明斯利啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍登上了衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以叛逃者的名義逮捕艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍在抓艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以必須趕快離開這顆衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊準備出航 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉和迪克也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生要我穿好機師服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和聯邦軍作對…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還多說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE確實可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是… 沒想到會和聯邦軍為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕的話 現在下船也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘 分清輕重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽時 偶爾也會遇上不利的車道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能丟掉必勝的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將從衛星內航行 轉換為外宇宙航行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統探測到艦船反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到識別信號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍所屬 達維恩級宇宙戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷 日暈 看守者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會以為那樣就結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想輕易逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些叛逃者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦艦隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來逮捕我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會被怎麼處置？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逮捕我們最好的辦法是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艦船開動前實施控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 天神號就無處可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這麼做就說明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個也別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍他們 艦船就是他們的監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真老老實實出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信滿滿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克不只是個優秀的電腦工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說還有過人的參謀企劃能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被提拔為阿雷克斯基地的副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得艦長也吃了他的虧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 那種憲兵隊的差事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不符合我的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵是 沒想到高達會來攪局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為軍艦上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這種情形更讓人興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮是可以 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心吃多上火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的大腦滿負荷運轉時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓我看看你的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體機動戰士準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}重複 全體機動戰士…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要打了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可都是聯邦軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要出動機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼陰謀嗎 古魯迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何應對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要跟著他們的節奏走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 焰火伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 信號彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼光？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光彈障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰術雖然略顯古典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作用卻一目瞭然不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線路接通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是地球聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八宇宙艦隊特別分遣艦隊司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特拉·葛瓦班中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經被完全包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即解除武裝 乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 就認定你們為敵對勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動總攻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用槍指著人家 還裝正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是擔任天神號航行總管的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當斯·提尼爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不打算與聯邦軍為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克艦長在個人調查中發現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE躲藏在被棄置的宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為 現在正是對UE發起反擊的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰一旦成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必能對UE造成重大打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 葛瓦班中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望第八宇宙艦隊網開一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你提供的情報很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是上級部門應該考慮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人不可以擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果還是個軍人就該明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是逮捕古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 給個答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不作答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫不得已 我們只能強制執行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先安排高達躲入衛星的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開索敵系統偵測
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的損失怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束槍被擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台Genoace安然無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝腔作勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 多半不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被艦隊的火控系統鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有部署在周圍的機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候出動的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光彈的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光彈發射後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用數台機動戰士牽制天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引我們注意力的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動了其他部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在被他們耍著玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 看你怎麼辦 古魯迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會老老實實投降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就算他們頑抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且擊沉我們一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘的兩艘必會擊沉天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根結底死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們已經扳回了劣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…還藏有艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊不久將歇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼停止攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會 因為同是聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心生憐憫了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還須前往攻略安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡可能避免消耗彈藥和艦隻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克的想法無非是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為另有目的 所以不想做無謂的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集結了這麼多戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他難道真打算去討伐UE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們必須履行職責
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 還有什麼招數？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊來自艦隊後方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙難道還有增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統沒有捕捉到任何目標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反應是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統捕捉到目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥艦2 機動戰士型10
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暈聯隊 機動戰士損失慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法維持戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓部署在前方的機動戰士回去增援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最優先保護艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮如果繼續對準天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被UE從背後攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果調頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後背又會暴露給天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八宇宙艦隊 正與UE交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是意想不到的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍就交給UE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開這個宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往安巴德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 對同胞見死不救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長不也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免消耗彈藥和艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是千載難逢的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 去營救敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再被抓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士部隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊眼前的UE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等這句話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付UE不用留情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號的機動戰士部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 這裏有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是安巴德的前哨站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我熱個身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去安巴德教訓UE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死在這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像能看見敵人的軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術不錯啊 天神號的機師們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號快速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱能傳感器確認主炮正在充能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜同歸於盡 想擊沉我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大戰速離開天神號主炮的軸線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的 拿我的船當掩護打敵人措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡日暈 看守者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艦隊司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦緊急調頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認射擊系統同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標更改為UE艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充填準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊射 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許給我停！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 那麼步調一致
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人戰艦及機動戰士型正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要命 總算趕跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你們救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄我們而去的話明明可以輕鬆逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在抗擊UE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有機會見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想與你喝一杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛逃者古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們與UE交戰間隙 趁亂逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是今天 在這裏發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 不必多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們好運 勇敢的叛逃者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中發生過這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我看見了敵人的行動軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像遇見柚鈴的那次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是XRounder的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說聯邦軍正在研究
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類大腦中 一塊掌管特殊能力的區域
